Did Jesus intend that this prayer be repeated word for word every time we pray, as is done by many in Christendom?
No.
Just before Jesus provided this prayer as a pattern, he said: When praying, do not say the same things over and over again.
On a later occasion, he restated this prayer but used different wording.
Thus Jesus helped us know what sort of things we need to ask for and in what order of importance.
Hence, it is fitting to call it the model prayer.
