Are you a young person who is considering baptism?
If so, what lies before you is the greatest privilege any human could have.
However, baptism is a serious step.
It symbolizes your dedication—a solemn promise you make to Jehovah that you will serve him forever by putting his will above everything else in your life.
Understandably, you should get baptized only when you are qualified to make that decision, you have a personal desire to do so, and you understand the meaning of dedication.
What if you are not sure that you are ready for baptism?
